3. cs.COMM (Communications and Networking) - The paper deals with communication channels and proposes a new communication scheme, which falls under the scope of communications and networking. 
4. cs.SI (Systems and Control) - The paper deals with the problem of interference in communication systems, which is a key area of research in systems and control.
